<h1>Word Count</h1>
<p>Word Count is a fun app that lets you enter a phrase and a search word and it will count how many time that search word appears in the phrase!</p>

<form action="/result">
  <div class="form-group">
    <h2>Enter Phrase:</h2>
    <input id="phrase" name="phrase" class="form-control" type="text">
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <h2>Enter Search Word:</h2>
    <input id="match_word" name="match_word" class="form-control" type="text">
  </div>
  <button type="submit" class="btn-success">Count Word</button>
</form>
